body:

Super Mario Maker 2 may still be a little over a month away but that hasn’t stopped Kit & Krysta from making SMM2 the focus of the latest Nintendo Minute. In their newest video, the pair discuss and design their very own levels that they wish to make in Super Mario Maker 2.

Kit goes with an outer Space theme for his level whereas Krysta puts the rising water level theme to good use.

body:
6 Sonic Characters Have New Voice Actors In Team Sonic Racing

The credits of Team Sonic Racinghave recently surfaced online, including the game’s voice overs. Footage of the game had already suggested that voices for Knuckles, Omochao, Silver, Blaze, Zavok and Omega had been changed, but the credits have confirmed it. Some voice actors, including Travis Willingham and Laura Bailey, are not mentioned. Instead, there are some new voice actors credited. A…

summary: Home.  Rules.  Message.  Masterlist.  Credit. Looking for a place where you can write your muses to your...
caption:
Home.  Rules.  Message.  Masterlist.  Credit.

Looking for a place where you can write your muses to your hearts’ content? Ever wonder if your OC will find a place to fit in? Then look no further!

                                  Welcome to the National Park !

We are a game-verse Pokémon RP group full of fun, friendly, and active members.  Our goal is to provide a comfortable atmosphere where members can write and develop their muses at their own pace, without all the stress of running an indie blog.

In addition to our community of wonderful writers, we offer frequent events, interactive Discord server, unlimited meme opportunities, and a special ‘Member of the Month’ spotlight!

We love welcoming new friends, so why not check us out today?
